newsitem.title: UK: One Brent kept, the other clocked - trade.
newsitem.headline: One Brent kept, the other clocked - trade.

text.p: One Brent cargo was kept from the paper chains on Thursday but a second went unclaimed at the five o'clock deadline, traders said.
Wall Street trader J.P. Morgan kept one of the cargoes, due to load December 20-22. The other cargo was clocked to Norway's Statoil.
